node.text:
Beautiful Switzerland🇨🇭
Switzerland has traditions too!❤️
During September, the happy alp life comes to an end and the cows are going down againinto the valleys🏔🐄
They wear the big bells  only on this event🔔🤗
📹: @michelphotographych 
.
.
.

2.Brienzer Rothorn Train 
3.Lake Brienz

5.Brienz

9.Wengen

node.text:
Wonderful Switzerland🇨🇭
The locations:
1: Engelberg
2: Lungern
3: Berner Oberland
4: Lauterbrunnen 
5: Swiss Alps
Which one is your favorite from 1-5?😍🏔☀️☕️🏡
📹: @world.from.my.eyes 
.
.
.

Beautiful Switzerland🇨🇭
We want to thank you very very much for 200k followers!🥳
We are so glad to show you the beauty of Switzerland every day!❤️
.
Stay tuned, many awesome things are coming!😄👌🏼
.
1: Lungern
2: Lauterbrunnen 
3: Uri, Stäuber Waterfall
4: Hotel (name unknown)
5: Lungern
6: Ennetbürgen
.
📹: @sennarelax 
.
.

Wonderful Switzerland🇨🇭😍🏔☕️🏨
Which one from 1-10 is your favorite?
📹: @sennarelax 
📍The Locations, to note where you would love to go next!
1. Uri
2. Zermatt
3.Stans Canton Luzern
4.Grindelwald 
5.Mürren 
6.Rheinfall Schaffhausen
7.Lauterbrunnen
8.Appenzell
9.Arolla 
10.Gstaad Canton Bern
.
.
.
